Description:
In the middle of a vast arena stands an altar with an ever-burning flame, surrounded by treasures. You can feel the heat from a distance, such is the power of the Great Bird. As you approach the altar, the flame intensifies, and you all feel as though its heat scorches part of your soul, momentarily stunning you. 

When you recover, there it is, the Great Bird, in all its glory. It stares at you, its gaze piercing your souls, judging you. There is nowhere to run or hide. 

Your only option is to move toward the Great Bird, perched on its altar, waiting for you.
DescriptionAction: Now, it is time to face the judgment of the Great Bird.
